 [ Click here to enter Back to the Roots ] Back to the Roots found its home at NVG.org An Amiga friendly networking group at the University of Trondheim, Norway. Please note: Back to the Roots is a 100% non profit project, we are a bunch of volunteers who maintain this project in their freetime with the help of numerous contributors . We all together donate large amounts of time, content, online costs, hardware, connectivity and bandwidth to provide you a high quality free service. If you like our work, then feel free to contribute : Please Donate some money or Contribute some work! We also run a Back to the Roots IRC channel provided by our friends at abime.net. Server: irc.back2roots.org - Port: 6667 - Channel: #back2roots 
